Hello KSP players,

I was looking for an FA-18 on these forums and decided to make on as I couldn't find a good one.

So I now present the BAE (Bajeebus Aeronautical Engineering) KA-18E SuperHornet

[Action Group 1] deploys the flaps

AS A WORD OF CAUTION: You probably don't want to mess with anything, the building techniques are messy in this craft and you could break it.

Here's the DL [http://www./download/3ugnl9an9804cac/FA-18E_Stock.craft](http://www./download/3ugnl9an9804cac/FA-18E_Stock.craft)

**Edited <time datetime="2015-06-09T22:42:32Z" title="06/09/2015 10:42  PM" data-short="9 yr">June 9, 2015</time> by JDarksword**
This is just amazing, JDarkSword! Great work ![:)](//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif)
Also if anyone has problems with the pre-coolers falling off let me know and I will add some hidden struts. For anyone who wants a modded version I can also release that, just let me know as well.
